        "## A.5 Common simulation patterns\n",
        "\n",
        "### White noise\n",
        "\n",
        "White noise has mean zero, constant variance, and zero autocovariance at nonzero lags."
      ],
      "id": "513a983a"
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "#| eval: false\n",
        "n = 400\n",
        "sigma = 1.0\n",
        "w = rng.normal(0, sigma, size=n)"
      ],
      "id": "1b02d371",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "### Random walk\n",
        "\n",
        "The random walk satisfies $X_t = X_{t-1} + W_t$."
      ],
      "id": "2ab31210"
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "#| eval: false\n",
        "x_rw = np.cumsum(w)"
      ],
      "id": "4744c46a",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "### AR(1)\n",
        "\n",
        "The AR(1) model is\n",
        "\n",
        "$$\n",
        "X_t = \\phi X_{t-1} + W_t.\n",
        "$$"
      ],
      "id": "9d5c5ce7"
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "#| eval: false\n",
        "n = 400\n",
        "burnin = 200\n",
        "total = n + burnin\n",
        "phi = 0.75\n",
        "w = rng.normal(0, 1, size=total)\n",
        "x_full = np.zeros(total)\n",
        "\n",
        "for t in range(1, total):\n",
        "    x_full[t] = phi * x_full[t - 1] + w[t]\n",
        "\n",
        "x_ar1 = x_full[burnin:]\n",
        "assert len(x_ar1) == n"
      ],
      "id": "45da791a",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "### MA(1)\n",
        "\n",
        "The MA(1) model is\n",
        "\n",
        "$$\n",
        "X_t = W_t + \\theta W_{t-1}.\n",
        "$$"
      ],
      "id": "a3247f48"
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "#| eval: false\n",
        "theta = 0.70\n",
        "x_full = np.zeros(total)\n",
        "\n",
        "for t in range(1, total):\n",
        "    x_full[t] = w[t] + theta * w[t - 1]\n",
        "\n",
        "x_ma1 = x_full[burnin:]\n",
        "assert len(x_ma1) == n"
